description:
This model was open sourced by Facebook AI Research. It is a Sequence-to-Sequence machine translation model that translates German to English.
 The model was published under the following license: https://github.com/pytorch/fairseq/blob/master/LICENSE
inputDescription:
Text to be translated.
For example: "Hallo, wie geht es dir?"
name: GermanToEnglish
projectDescription: Models that use Neural Machine Translation to translate text from one language to another.
